with injury that turned out to be a back bruise. United Press International; 
Photo, Detroit's Bill Laimbeer grabs nothing but air as Orlando Woolridge hauls 
in a rebound in the fourth quarter of Lakers' 107-97 victory. Associated Press 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
