GERMANY; POLLUTION -- POLAND; POLLUTION -- CZECHOSLOVAKIA; ENVIRONMENT; 
INDUSTRIAL EMISSIONS; HEALTH STATISTICS; CZECHOSLOVAKIA -- HEALTH; TEPLICE 
(CZECHOSLOVAKIA) 
</P>
