<P>
TEACHERS -- CALIFORNIA; CALIFORNIA -- SCHOOLS -- FINANCES; CALIFORNIA TEACHERS 
ASSOCIATION; GOVERNMENT SPENDING; CALIFORNIA -- CONSTITUTIONS; CALIFORNIA -- 
EDUCATION; CALIFORNIA -- ELECTIONS -- 1990; PROPOSITION 98 (SCHOOL DISTRICT 
FUNDS); GASOLINE; EXCISE TAX -- CALIFORNIA 
</P>
