<DATELINE>
<P>
MELBOURNE, Australia 
</P>
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Yannick Noah, Henri Leconte, Guy Forget and Jean Fleurian were named to the 
French Davis Cup squad today to face Australia in a first-round match on the 
grass courts at Royal Kings Park in Perth on Feb. 2-4. 
</P>
<P>
French Tennis Federation officials announced the team at the Australian Open. 
</P>
