<P>
January 22, 1990, Monday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<P>
DAVE MCCOY 
</P>
<SECTION>
<P>
Sports; Part C; Page 10; Column 1; Sports Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
<P>
3171 words 
</P>
